    %h5 The Puzzle School Exploration
    %p
      We are in the early stages of exploring a new upper or alternative high school
      in Cambridge.
    %p
      The "puzzle" metaphor is about a process rather than a specific design.
      The process consists of deep observations, developing and testing hypotheses,
      and seeking feedback as you make progress toward your goal.
    %p
      This process will inform all aspects of The Puzzle School, from how the school is run to the
      student's day-to-day experience to how students approach their own learning.
    %p
      You can read more in this
      = link_to('pdf description', 'PuzzleSchoolDescription.pdf', target: '_blank')
      of The Puzzle School.

